snippet.title: DRAGON BALL PROJECT : Multi - Regional β Test Trailer
snippet.description:
DRAGON BALL PROJECT : Multi

Stand Together, Win Together!
The Dragon Ball franchise's first 4v4 team-oriented battle begins!
---------
▼Regional β Test Details
Period: Aug. 20th, 6:00am - Sep. 3rd, 5:59am (UTC)
Test Regions: Canada, France, Germany, Japan, South Korea, Taiwan, United Kingdom, United States
Available Platform: iOS, Google Play, Steam(R)
